      <description>&lt;p&gt;&#xA;그간 심혈을 기울여 작업해온 테마를 공개하기로 결심했다. 힘든&#xA;결심이었지만, 나 또한 한사람의 ‘영포티’로서 大義를 위해 어쩔 수&#xA;없었다.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&#xA;👉 &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/ageldama/young40er-hugo-theme/&#34;&gt;Github Repo.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div id=&#34;outline-container-headline-1&#34; class=&#34;outline-2&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;headline-1&#34;&gt;&#xA;자랑스러운 스크린샷 모음&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;div id=&#34;outline-text-headline-1&#34; class=&#34;outline-text-2&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;figure&gt;&#xA;    &lt;img src=&#34;https://ageldama.github.io/posts/2025-12dec/young40er-hugo-theme-1st-rel/top.png&#34; width=&#34;&#34; alt=&#34;frontpage&#34; border=&#34;3&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;img src=&#34;https://ageldama.github.io/posts/2025-12dec/young40er-hugo-theme-1st-rel/pagination.png&#34; width=&#34;&#34; alt=&#34;pagination&#34; border=&#34;3&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;img src=&#34;https://ageldama.github.io/posts/2025-12dec/young40er-hugo-theme-1st-rel/single-top.png&#34; width=&#34;&#34; alt=&#34;single / top&#34; border=&#34;3&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;img src=&#34;https://ageldama.github.io/posts/2025-12dec/young40er-hugo-theme-1st-rel/single-tags.png&#34; width=&#34;&#34; alt=&#34;single / tags&#34; border=&#34;3&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;img src=&#34;https://ageldama.github.io/posts/2025-12dec/young40er-hugo-theme-1st-rel/archive-categories+tags.png&#34; width=&#34;&#34; alt=&#34;archive / categories+tags&#34; border=&#34;3&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;img src=&#34;https://ageldama.github.io/posts/2025-12dec/young40er-hugo-theme-1st-rel/archive-chrono.png&#34; width=&#34;&#34; alt=&#34;archive / chrono&#34; border=&#34;3&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;figcaption&gt;뿌듯하다.&lt;/figcaption&gt;&#xA;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
